<StringTableFile>
  <Name>conversations\08_wilderness\08_si_rhemen_broken_stairs</Name>
  <NextEntryID>1</NextEntryID>
  <EntryCount>10</EntryCount>
  <Entries>
    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>The stairs have collapsed, leaving a long drop to the floor below.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Leave.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Look below.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>The lower floor is dark, but you see puddles of water and fungi growing on the stone surfaces.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>8</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Anchor a grappling hook to the edge and climb down.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>9</ID>
      <DefaultText>As you slide down the rope, the rushing of water rumbles in your ears. It sounds as though the lake from the gorge is still draining into some distant reservoir.

Suddenly, a violent tremor rocks the cavern, and you feel your grip loosen from the rope.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>10</ID>
      <DefaultText>You secure a grappling hook to a cleft in the broken stairs and toss the line down.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>11</ID>
      <DefaultText>However, you manage to cling to the line until the quakes subside.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>12</ID>
      <DefaultText>[SkillCheck 0]'s hands release their grip on the rope, and [SkillCheck 0] plummets, landing face-first on the wet floor.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>13</ID>
      <DefaultText>You reach the bottom, your feet splashing in a puddle of water.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
  </Entries>
</StringTableFile>